Privacy Policy

At Zonamap, we value your privacy. This document outlines how we collect, use, and protect your personal data:

	1.	Information Collection: We may collect personal information, such as your name, email, and location, to enhance your experience on our platform.
	2.	Data Usage: Your data is used to provide property insights, document access, and real estate services. We do not sell or share your data with third parties without consent.
	3.	Security Measures: We use advanced encryption and secure servers to safeguard your information.
	4.	Your Rights: You can access, modify, or delete your data at any time by contacting us at privacy@zonamap.in.
	5.	Cookies: We use cookies to enhance website functionality and improve user experience.
